\b0 \cf0 I referenced {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://processing.org/examples/gameoflife.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 \ul \ulc2 https://processing.org/examples/gameoflife.html}} for the basic idea of the Game of Life.\
