\f1 Describe the biological significance of the additions you make. \uc0\u8232 \
\pard\pardeftab720\ri720

\b0 \cf0 The biological significance I attempted to make was a model of an infectious disease based on contact inhibition. This is a simple biological example of a viral infection that kills cells and co-exists in the system based on set rules.
\f2 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\ri720

\f1\b \cf0 Describe the technical significance of the additions you make. \uc0\u8232 \
\pard\pardeftab720\ri720

\b0 \cf0 I would consider my data visualization techniques technically significant. It was challenging to make a line plot, but I figured it was similar to the idea of the cell array, where it initializes an array of values and then fills the array based on new cell counts. The sliders were a little bit simpler to add. I also designed the canvas to effectively use white space, be appropriate complementary colors, and be a stand-alone interactive application.
\f2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\ri720

